oldref="13">Microsoft PowerPoint 97/2000/XP</paragraph>
<paragraph xml-lang="en-US" id="par_id3148922" role="paragraph" l10n="U" oldref="14">Specifies the settings for documents in Microsoft PowerPoint.</paragraph>
